div1.p: Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss: I E.F. Whittier Sheriff of Spokane County, W.T. do hereby certify that I hold the above named William C. Swartz, by virtue of the answered mittimus, and that I have none the said Swartz before the said the Honorable George Turner Judge, at his chambers Witness my hand this 14th day of August A.D. 1885. E.F. Whittier Sheriff of Spokane County W.T.
Sheriffs Fees August 14th one service 1.00 Mileage 32 3.20 One days attachments 3.00 from Spokane 2.00 3 miles 1.50 Received by order of court $10.70 1.00 11.70

Territory of Washington Plaintiff vs. Wm C. Swartz Defendant
Writ of Habeas Corpus
Issued August 13 1885
Returned & filed August 14, 1885 D.A. Clement Clerk
